<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.4.4">
<l>oṉṟiya tiṅkaḷaik kāṭṭi yoḷimaṇi vaṇṇaṉē yeṉṉu</l>
<l>niṉṟa kuṉṟattiṉai nōkki neṭumālē, vāveṉṟu kūvu</l>
<l>naṉṟupey yumaḻai kāṇi ṉāraṇaṉ vantā ṉeṉṟālu</l>
<l>meṉṟiṉ maiyalkaḷ ceytā reṉṉuṭaik kōmaḷat taiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Pointing at the moon that resembles [him] she says “the one of bright sapphire colour”,</l>
<l>looking at the hill that stands she cooes “great Māl, come!”,</l>
<l>when she sees the rains that pour down well she dances, saying “Nāraṇaṉ”.</l>
<l>When did he cause sweet madnesses in my tender [girl]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
